Package app

package app
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    App
    Main entry point for the JavaFX application that loads the login view from an FXML file.
    CartItem
    Represents an item being added to the cart including different drink, topping, and customization options.
    CashierController
    Controller class for creating orders on the cashier's view.
    Database
    Class for managing database connections.
    Drink
    Represents a drink that can be ordered.
    DrinkVariation
    Represents a specific variation of a drink with customizable attributes.
    Employee
    Represents an Employee at the store with their own credentials.
    EmployeeController
    Controller responsible for managing employee data in the Employee View.
    Ingredient
    Represents an ingredient used in a recipe or inventory system.
    InventoryController
    Controller class for the Inventory Management view.
    LoginController
    Controller for the login screen to sign in as manager or cashier.
    ManagerController
    Handles management features in the application such as employee management and drink price updates.
    ReturnsController
    Controller for the returns system on the cashier view.
    SalesController
    Controller class for managing the sales view for the POS system.
    Supply
    Represents a supply item in the inventory.
    Topping
    Represents a topping that can be added to a drink.
